[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0694","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0694.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0454","title":"多厂商 TCP/IP 远程操作系统指纹识别漏洞","description":"远程攻击者可向目标主机发送特制的 IP 或 ICMP 数据包，根据目标系统对数据包的响应差异（如初始 TTL 值、IP 分片行为、ICMP 回显应答特征等）识别其操作系统类型，这种技术被称为 TCP/IP 协议栈指纹识别。利用 nmap、queso 等工具可实现自动化检测，广泛影响各类操作系统和网络设备。该漏洞虽不直接导致代码执行或数据泄露，但暴露了目标系统信息，降低了后续针对性攻击的门槛。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0454"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:25.877","remediation":"在网络边界防火墙上配置规则，丢弃不必要的 ICMP 报文（如 ICMP Timestamp、Address Mask 请求），阻止探测流量进入内网。对外服务的服务器应使用 TCP 栈参数加固工具（如 sysctl 调整 net.ipv4.tcp_timestamps=0），减少特征泄露。非必要情况下避免直接暴露主机至公网，改用反向代理或 NAT 隐藏真实操作系统指纹。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2048"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0694.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0693","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0693.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0453","title":"Cisco 设备 CDP 协议信息泄露漏洞","description":"Cisco 设备的发现协议（CDP，Cisco Discovery Protocol）在 UDP 端口 1999 上运行，但该端口同时也会响应 TCP SYN 探测包。远程攻击者无需任何认证即可向目标 Cisco 路由器发送 TCP SYN 数据包至 1999 端口，根据回应判断设备是否为 Cisco 设备，从而识别内网中的 Cisco 设备型号与存在性。该漏洞属于信息泄露类型（CWE-200），攻击者利用此漏洞可进一步收集目标网络资产信息，为后续针对性攻击做准备。该漏洞影响大量 Cisco 路由器设备，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0453"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:25.710","remediation":"在 Cisco IOS 设备全局配置模式下执行 `no cdp run` 禁用 Cisco Discovery Protocol，或在不受信任的接口下执行 `no cdp enable` 关闭该接口的 CDP 通告；如因网络管理需求必须保留 CDP，可配置扩展 ACL 拒绝入站 TCP SYN 访问端口 1999，同时结合 `control-plane` 策略限速该端口的异常流量。对于老旧 IOS 版本，建议升级至仍受支持的 IOS 版本以获取更完善的访问控制能力。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0453"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0693.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0692","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0692.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0452","title":"开源应用程序开发者内置后门漏洞","description":"该漏洞源于开发者在某服务或应用程序中故意放置了后门密码。攻击者可利用该后门密码直接远程登录目标系统，从而完全控制受影响的服务或应用，实现机密信息窃取、数据篡改和拒绝服务等操作。CVSS v2 评分为 10.0，攻击复杂度低，无需身份认证，危害等级严重。此类后门问题通常存在于软件开发和调试阶段未移除的默认凭据中。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0452"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:25.590","remediation":"立即审计受影响应用的源代码及配置文件，查找并移除所有硬编码的后门账户/密码凭据。同时更改应用的默认管理员密码为强密码，并在网络边界防火墙配置访问控制规则（ACL），限制对该服务端口（如 22/80/443/自定义端口）的源 IP 范围。若厂商已发布安全更新版本，应优先升级至修复版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0452"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0692.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0683","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0683.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0448","title":"Microsoft IIS 4 日志绕过漏洞","description":"IIS 4.0 存在日志绕过漏洞，远程攻击者可通过发送超长的 HTTP 请求方法（method）来隐藏其真正请求的 URL，导致攻击行为无法被日志完整记录。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 平台上的 IIS 4.0 服务器，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用此漏洞隐藏恶意行为，增加追踪溯源难度。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0448"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:25.087","remediation":"升级到 Windows 2000 及以上版本（IIS 5.0+），新版 IIS 能正确记录完整 HTTP 请求方法及 URL。对于仍需兼容旧系统的环境，可部署反向代理或 WAF 进行外层请求日志审计，确保所有请求方法均被记录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0448","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19149"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0683.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0639","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0639.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0399","title":"mIRC DCC 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"mIRC 5.5 客户端 DCC 服务器命令在处理文件名时未正确过滤特殊字符，远程攻击者可通过向目标用户发送特制的 DCC 文件传输请求，利用路径遍历或命令注入手法将恶意文件写入非预期目录，从而在受害者的系统上执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 mIRC 5.5 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。用户接收 DCC 文件时即可能触发，无需额外认证。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0399"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:18.833","remediation":"立即升级 mIRC 客户端至 5.6 或更高版本（5.5 及更早版本存在文件名字符过滤缺陷）。如无法升级，请在 mIRC 设置中关闭 DCC 自动接收功能，并避免接受来自不可信来源的 DCC 文件传输请求。此外，可在防火墙或路由器层面阻止 IRC 常用端口（6660-6669/TCP）的不必要入站连接作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0399"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0639.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0637","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0637.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0398","title":"SSH Communications Security SSH 服务器过期帐户认证绕过漏洞","description":"tags.<value>SSH 1.2.27 和 2.0.11 版本在 Linux 系统中存在身份认证绕过漏洞，已过期的用户账户仍可通过 SSH 服务正常登录系统。攻击者可利用该漏洞通过已过期账户获取系统未授权访问权限，可能导致敏感信息泄露或进一步攻击。该漏洞影响运行上述 SSH 版本的 Linux 系统，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。建议升级到不受影响的 SSH 版本以修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0398"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:18.677","remediation":"立即升级到 OpenSSH 3.0p1 及以上版本，或升级到 SSH 2.3.0 及以上版本。旧版 SSH 1.x/2.0.x 存在多项已知漏洞且已停止维护。如无法升级，可在 SSH 服务端配置文件 /etc/ssh/sshd_config 中设置 PermitEmptyPasswords no 和 UsePAM yes，启用 PAM 认证以强制检查账户过期状态。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0398"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0637.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0634","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0634.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0395","title":"BackWeb Polite Agent Protocol 竞争条件欺骗漏洞","description":"BackWeb Polite Agent Protocol 存在竞争条件漏洞，远程攻击者可通过利用协议中的时间差漏洞，伪装成合法的 BackWeb 服务器实施欺骗攻击，导致客户端被误导连接至恶意服务器。攻击者可借此实现中间人攻击或向用户推送恶意内容。该漏洞影响使用 BackWeb 技术的系统，CVSS 评分 5.1，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0395"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:18.303","remediation":"建议立即升级 BackWeb Polite Agent 至官方补丁版本，修复协议握手过程中的竞态条件漏洞，防止攻击者通过抢占时序窗口伪造服务器身份。如无法升级，可在防火墙上限制仅允许与已知可信 BackWeb 服务器通信，并对接收内容进行数字签名校验。鉴于该产品已停止维护，建议彻底卸载 BackWeb Polite Agent 并迁移至其他受支持的软件分发方案。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://xforce.iss.net/alerts/advise17.php"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0634.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0598","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0598.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0364","title":"Microsoft Access 97 数据库密码明文存储漏洞","description":"Microsoft Access 97 存在数据库密码明文存储漏洞，该软件在创建受密码保护的数据库时，将用户设置的数据库密码以未经加密的明文形式写入外部的 MDB 文件头部区域。本地攻击者通过文本编辑器或十六进制查看工具直接打开该 MDB 文件即可从文件二进制数据中提取完整的数据库密码，从而绕过身份验证机制完全访问受保护的数据库内容。该漏洞源于 Access 97 在设计时未对存储的密码进行加密处理，影响 Microsoft Access 97 所有版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。建议用户升级至更高版本 Microsoft Office 或使用第三方加密工具对数据库文件进行额外保护。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0364"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:14.247","remediation":"Microsoft Access 97 已停止支持多年，建议立即迁移至受支持的 Microsoft 365 或 Office 2021 等现代版本。如暂时无法迁移，避免在共享网络位置存放含密码的 .mdb 文件，并使用 Windows EFS 或 BitLocker 对数据库文件所在目录进行加密，同时将数据库密码替换为 Windows 集成身份验证。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91816470220259&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0364.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0364","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0364.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0364.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hvp5-q7xm-fj7p/GHSA-hvp5-q7xm-fj7p.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0364.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--80c82ddc-bc10-4574-98b0-fe5e3ff3aadf.json","https://github.com/Christopher0129/security-knowledge-base/blob/ecec748afe5bbe2fcd2fd04b00fb46bc827b2c5d/system-vulnerabilities/windows.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0598.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0592","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0592.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0361","title":"LaserFiche NetWare 版敏感信息泄露漏洞","description":"LaserFiche for NetWare 版本以明文形式存储用户名和密码，导致邻近网络的攻击者可通过访问系统文件获取管理员凭证，造成敏感信息泄露。同时，系统允许管理员配置更改但未记录日志，使得未授权操作无法追溯审计。攻击者可利用窃取的凭证对系统进行进一步未授权访问与控制。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0361"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:13.863","remediation":"升级到 LaserFiche 现代版本（如 9.0 以上）以使用加密存储和审计日志功能；若无法升级，迁移至 Hyland 或其他具备加密存储与操作审计的文档管理平台。作为临时缓解措施，在网络层限制对 LaserFiche 服务的访问来源，仅允许受信任管理 IP 连接，并在 NetWare 服务器上启用文件系统和操作审计日志。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0361","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0361.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0361","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0361.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0361.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7ch8-6pch-qhqg/GHSA-7ch8-6pch-qhqg.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0361.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82496/info.html","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000420.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--106f99f3-e05b-4e49-be82-91767e97aac7.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0592.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0586","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0586.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0355","title":"CA ControlIT 4.5 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"CA ControlIT 4.5 存在拒绝服务漏洞，本地或远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标系统的 ControlIT 服务发送特制请求，导致目标系统强制重启或强制已有用户会话注销，造成服务不可用。该漏洞影响 CA ControlIT 4.5 版本，攻击者可通过网络远程触发，无需复杂前置条件即可实现拒绝服务攻击。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0355"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:13.103","remediation":"CA ControlIT 4.5 已停止维护，建议迁移至厂商当前支持的远程管理解决方案。临时缓解措施：在防火墙上限制仅允许受信任 IP 访问 ControlIT 服务端口（默认 TCP 1499），并禁用不必要的远程控制功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0355","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0355.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0355","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0355.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0355.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jqgq-vf46-2wc2/GHSA-jqgq-vf46-2wc2.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0355.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82468/info.html","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000419.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--86340522-28cc-4ec8-9d76-b049bcd8b6d2.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0586.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0476","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0476.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0286","title":"Microsoft Windows NT Web 服务器源代码泄露漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统的 Web 服务器存在源代码泄露漏洞。远程攻击者通过在 URL 末尾添加一个空格字符，可绕过服务器对动态页面（如 ASP）的访问限制，从而读取活动页面的源代码。该漏洞允许攻击者获取数据库连接字符串、业务逻辑等敏感信息，为后续攻击提供信息基础，无需身份认证即可远程利用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0286"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:04.477","remediation":"安装 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 4 (SP4) 或更高版本，该更新已修复 IIS 对 URL 末尾空格的解析问题。如无法升级，可在 IIS 管理器中禁用不必要的脚本映射（如 .htr），或使用 URLScan 工具过滤包含空格的请求作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0286","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0286.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0286","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0286.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0286.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0286.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mcjx-hw8r-r6gf/GHSA-mcjx-hw8r-r6gf.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0286.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--66533299-dc62-42f2-95a8-8fa5e27069d0.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/7ae10c2036875bb5ef530e18322e7ca2477ed16c/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0476.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0475","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0475.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0285","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 Resource Kit Telnet 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 Resource Kit 中包含的 telnet 工具存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，只需向目标系统的 telnet 服务发起连接后立即关闭该连接，即可导致 telnet 服务进程崩溃或资源耗尽，造成目标系统无法正常提供 telnet 服务。该漏洞影响 Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 系统，攻击复杂度低，利用方式简单，无需任何前置权限。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0285"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:04.357","remediation":"立即卸载 Windows NT 4.0 Resource Kit 中的 telnet.exe 工具，或将其重命名/移出系统路径以阻止调用。对于仍须使用 telnet 服务的环境，在防火墙层面限制仅信任 IP 可访问 23 端口，并升级到受支持的 Windows Server 版本（如 Windows Server 2019/2022）以彻底规避该问题。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0285","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0285.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0285.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0285","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0285.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0285.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jf86-639r-gxrp/GHSA-jf86-639r-gxrp.json","https://github.com/